task: S03 T4 — #651 Cart line SKU: plumb sku field + fix display (NHL-{partnumber})
requires: [NEXTJS_VERCEL_FRONTEND]
sprint: S03
repos: [crop-front]
branch: issue-651

context: |
  John call 2026-05-04: cart line shows duplicate model/brand/part — should show
  canonical NHL-{partnumber} SKU format (NOT NHL-P; the "P" was a transcription error).
  Audit-confirmed root cause against dev:
  - Part type has sku (lib/search-service/types/part.ts:189) — PRESENT in API
  - CartItem type has sku? (lib/stores/cart-store.ts:26) — field exists
  - PDP handleAddToCart (app/parts/[id]/_components/product-detail.tsx:177) does NOT
    pass sku into addItem() — sku: undefined on every cart line added from PDP
  - Catalog card (product-card-add-to-cart.tsx) also missing sku — same gap
  - cart-item-card.tsx:347-354 already renders: {manufacturer} · {item.sku ?? item.partNumber}
    — display logic is correct, just falls through to partNumber because sku is always undefined
  External dep: hub#63 (Alex) must be MERGED before this PR lands
  — sku column must be live in parts_public / search MV so the API actually returns it.
  Seq dep: branch off AFTER T3 (issue-650) is merged to dev, since both touch
  product-card-add-to-cart.tsx. If T3 PR is not yet merged, branch off dev and
  coordinate with T3 to avoid conflicts.

steps:
  1. Branch: git checkout -b issue-651 dev (after T3 is merged)
  2. Before fix — repro artifact:
     - Find a part with a known SKU: GET /api/parts/{pn} → check sku field in response
     - Add to cart from PDP → open /cart → screenshot showing partNumber fallback
       instead of NHL- prefix. Post as comment on #651.
  3. Fix — plumb sku through add-to-cart payloads:
     a. app/parts/[id]/_components/product-detail.tsx:177 — add sku: product.sku
        to the addItem() call alongside imageUrl, title, etc.
     b. features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.tsx — add sku: part.sku
        to the addItem() call (T3 already touches this file — coordinate).
  4. Sweep sibling surfaces per issue:
     - /checkout/review line items — does it also render sku? If so, verify.
     - Order confirmation page + email line items — note for John if sku not shown there.
     - Pack-alias lines (CT-NHL-{PN}-PK{N}, front#919) — MUST NOT regress; run existing tests.
  5. Unit tests:
     a. addItem payload for PDP includes sku: product.sku
     b. cart-item-card render: given sku: "NHL-12345678" → subtitle shows NHL-12345678;
        given sku: undefined → falls back to partNumber (existing behavior preserved)
     c. Pack-alias tests (front#919) still green.
  6. Commit: fix(cart): plumb sku field into add-to-cart payloads for NHL-{pn} display (#651)
     NOTE: Do NOT merge PR until hub#63 is confirmed merged by Alex.
  7. Open draft PR into dev, reference #651 + hub#63, include repro artifact.

external_gate: |
  hub#63 (Alex) — adds parts.sku as GENERATED column {brand_code}-{part_number} in PG,
  propagates via parts_public / search MV. FE work is ready to land but MUST NOT merge
  before hub#63 is confirmed live (or the sku field will always be undefined in prod).

cmd:
  - bun run lint:fix
  - bun run type-check
  - bunx vitest run app/parts/\[id\]/_components/product-detail.test.tsx
  - bunx vitest run app/cart/_components/cart-item-card.test.tsx
  - bunx vitest run features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.test.tsx

out:
  - app/parts/[id]/_components/product-detail.tsx (sku added to addItem payload)
  - features/catalog/product-card-add-to-cart.tsx (sku added to addItem payload)
  - app/cart/_components/cart-item-card.test.tsx (sku display + fallback test)
  - issue #651 comment with repro artifact

done:
  - Cart line subtitle shows NHL-{partnumber} (not raw partNumber) when sku is present
  - Subtitle falls back to partNumber when sku: undefined (no regression)
  - Pack-alias (front#919) tests green
  - vitest suite green, lint + type-check clean
  - PR draft open against dev, marked NOT READY with note: awaiting hub#63
